name: My Skyzone game
description:
To win the level, get to the yellow circle, you have 20 seconds

Freestyle only lasts for a hour, so we put mini games

Trophy guide

All you can jump - unlock every trophy

Dodgeball - Beat dodgeball 2

Sandpit - Beat sandpit

Speed run - Beat pool

Warrior - Beat warrior

Freestyle - Make it to the freestyle stage

Good - Beat the game

Score breaker - win the tournament

Welcome - Play the game

Squid - Beat the squid game

Stop and go - Play the squid game

Boring trip - Start the game then imediently press m

??? - find the secret map
